sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService created)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read InferenceService details<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RBAC resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create KEDA TriggerAuthentication<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService ready

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-nim-opendatahub-io-v1-account<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Read NGC API key Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Secret data
    Webhook->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Webhook: Validation response
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response (admit/reject)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Account created)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM ServingRuntime Template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Image Pull Secret<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: Account ready

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Webhook Admission Control

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Pod<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>Auth: K8s API client cert (mTLS)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec
    K8sAPI-->>User: Pod created/updated

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
